Title: The path that found me
DateModified: '2019-03-09'
DatePublished: '2019-03-09'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-path-that-found-me
SetInCountry: Spain
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Claudia  Phantshi
AuthorCountry: South Africa
Text: "It\u2019s based on an impulse I followed. I had to trust that I was going to\
  \ be ok venturing to a world that has only been in my dreams, a world with a language\
  \ that my conscious mind could not understand, yet me soul did. It was this world\u2019\
  s call to my soul that helped me take the risk, alone I abondened my comfort and\
  \ security and travelled to a foreign country, my home country, my soul\u2019s home\
  \ country, Spain. The smells haunted me, I knew I was there for not just travelling\
  \ alone. I was there to reunite with my soulmate, the one with whom I shared many\
  \ lives of love."
